0.4rc6a: Crashes-causing illegal-free() bug fixed. 

0.4rc6: Memory leaks fixed.

0.4rc5: Fixed the non-square-image generation bug in the FFT.
	Fixed the first-row-first-column bug.

0.4rc4: Fixed broken installation in Debian and Ubuntu

